## Strict Sequential Mode (Enforced)

This document is SECTION-GATED. Produce exactly one section per turn and wait for explicit approval before moving on.

### Hard Rules
- Only one section per turn. If asked to "전체 작성", refuse and ask which section to start.
- Use approval phrase to proceed with SECTION TITLE (not numbers).
- Keep process/gate messages in chat, not in the document.

### Per-Section Pre-Work Report (Short)
- Goal: "섹션 N 초안 작성"
- Scope: that section only
- Approach: 2-3 bullets
- Rule Applied: `.cursor/rules/07-테스트계획-규칙.mdc`

